quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  12,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  12,1,"a, l-, ray yeh uss kitaab ki ayaat hain jo apna mudda saaf saaf bayan karti hai"
  12,2,hum ne usay nazil kya hai quran bana kar arabi zabaan mein taakay tum ( ahal arab ) is ko achi terhan samajh sakuu
  12,3,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum is quran ko tumhari taraf wahi kar ke behtareen perayamein waqeat aur haqayiq tum se bayan karte hain, warna is se pehlay to ( un chizon se ) tum bilkul hi be khabar thay"
  12,4,"yeh uss waqt ka zikar hai jab yousuf ne apne baap se kaha"" abba jaan, mein ne khawab dekha hai ke gayarah setaaray hain aur Sooraj aur chaand hain aur woh mujhe sajda kar rahay hain """
  12,5,"jawab mein is ke baap ne kaha,"" beta, apna yeh khawab apne bhaiyon ko nah sunana warna woh tairay darpay azaar ho jayen ge, haqeeqat yeh hai ke shetan aadmi ka khula dushman hai"
  12,6,"aur aisa hi hoga ( jaissa to ne khawab mein dekha hai ke ) tera rab tujhe ( apne kaam ke liye ) muntakhib kere ga aur tujhe baton ki teh taq pohanchna sikhayiye ga aur tairay oopar aur all yaqoob par apni Nemat isi terhan poori kere ga jis terhan is se pehlay woh tairay buzurgon, ibrahim aur ishaq par kar chuka hai, yaqeenan tera rab Aleem aur hakeem hai """
  12,7,haqeeqat yeh hai ke yousuf aur is ke bhaiyon ke qissa mein inn poochnay walon ke liye barri nishanain hain
  12,8,"yeh qissa yun shuru hota hai ke is ke bhaiyon ne aapas mein kaha"" yeh yousuf aur is ka bhai, dono hamaray waalid ko hum sab se ziyada mehboob hain halaank hum aik poora jatha hain sachhi baat yeh hai ke hamaray abba jaan ba lkl hi behak gay hain"
  12,9,"chalo yousuf ko qatal kar do ya usay kahin pheink do taakay tumahray waalid ki tavajja sirf tumhari hi taraf ho jaye yeh kaam kar lainay ke baad phir naik ban rehna """
  12,10,"is par un mein se aik bola"" yousuf ko qatal nah karo, agar kuch karna hi hai to usay kisi andhay kunvey mein daal do koi aata jata qaafla usay nikaal le jaye ga """
  12,11,"is qarardad par unhon ne ja kar apne baap se kaha"" abba jaan, kya baat hai ke aap yousuf ke maamla mein hum par bharosa nahi karte halaank hum is ke sachey kher khuwa hain ?"
  12,12,"kal usay hamaray sath bhaij dijiya ga kuch churcug le ga aur khail kood se bhi dil behlaye ga hum is ki hifazat ko mojood hain """
  12,13,"baap ne kaha"" tumhara usay le jana mujhe shaq guzarta hai aur mujh ko andesha hai ke kahin usay bheria nah phaar kha ye jabkay tum is se ghaafil ho """
  12,14,"unhon ne jawab diya"" agar hamaray hotay usay bhir yai ne kha liya, jabkay hum aik jatha hain, tab to hum barray hi nikammay hon ge """
  12,15,"iss terhan israar kar ke jab woh ussay le gay aur unhon ne tey kar liya ke usay aik andhay kunvey mein chore den, to hum ne yousuf ko wahi ki ke"" aik waqt aeye ga jab to un logon ko un ki yeh harkat jitye ga, yeh apne feal ke nataij se be khabar hain """
  12,16,shaam ko woh rotay pitte apne baap ke paas aeye
  12,17,"aur kaha"" abba jaan, hum daud ka muqaabla karne mein lag gay thay aur yousuf ko hum ne apne samaan ke paas chore diya tha ke itnay mein bheria aa kar ussay kha gaya aap hamari baat ka yaqeen nah karen ge chahay hum sachey hi hon """
  12,18,"aur woh yousuf ke kameez par jhoot moot ka khoon laga kar aeye thay yeh sun kar un ke baap ne kaha"" balkay tumahray nafs ne tumahray liye aik barray kaam ko aasaan bana diya acha, sabr karoon ga aur bakhoobi karoon ga, jo baat tum bana rahay ho is par Allah hi se madad mangi ja sakti hai """
  12,19,"idhar aik qaafla aaya aur uss ne apne saqqay (water carrier) ko pani laane ke liye bheja saqqay (water carrier) ne jo kunvey (well) mein doll dala to ( yousuf ko dekh kar ) pukaar utha"" mubarak ho, yahan to aik larka hai"" un logon ne is ko maal tijarat samajh kar chhupa liya, halaank jo kuch woh kar rahay thay khuda is se bakhabar tha"
  12,20,aakhir-kaar unhon ne is ko thori si qeemat par chanddarhamonke iwaz beech dala aur woh is ki qeemat ke maamla mein kuch ziyada ke umeed waar nah thay
  12,21,"misar ke jis shakhs ne usay khareeda is ne apni biwi se kaha"" iss ko achi terhan rakhna, baeed nahi ke yeh hamaray liye mufeed saabit ho ya hum usay beta bana len"" is terhan hum ne yousuf ke liye uss sarzamen mein qadam jamanay ki soorat nikaali aur usay maamla fehmi ki taleem dainay ka intizam kya Allah apna kaam kar ke rehta hai, magar aksar log jantay nahi hain"
  12,22,"aur jab woh apni poori jawani ko pouncha to hum ne usay qowat faisla aur ilm ataa kya, iss terhan hum naik logon ko jaza dete hain"
  12,23,"jis aurat ke ghar mein woh tha woh uss par dooray daalnay lagi aur aik roz darwazay band kar ke boli"" aa ja"" yousuf ne kaha"" khuda ki panah, mere rab ne to mujhe achi manzilat bakhsh ( aur mein yeh kaam karoon! ) aisay zalim kabhi Falah nahi paaya karte """
  12,24,"woh uss ki taraf barhi aur yousuf bhi is ki taraf barhta agar apne rab ki Burhan nah dekh laita aisa howa, taakay hum is se badi aur be hiyai ko daur kar den, Dur haqeeqat woh hamaray chuney hue bundon mein se tha"
  12,25,"aakhir-kaar yousuf aur woh agay peechay darwazay ki taraf bhage aur is ne peechay se yousuf ka kameez ( khech kar ) phaar diya darwazay par dono ne is ke shohar ko mojood paaya usay dekhte hi aurat kehnay lagi,"" kya saza hai is shakhs ki jo teri ghar wali par niyat kharab kere? iss ke siwa aur kya saza hosakti hai ke woh qaid kya jaye ya usay sakht azaab diya jaye """
  12,26,"yousuf ne kaha"" yahi mujhe phansnay ki koshish kar rahi thi"" is aurat ke apne kunba walon mein seshakhs ne ( qareene ki ) shahadat paish ki ke"" agar yousuf ka kameez agay se phataa ho to aurat sachhi hai aur yeh jhoota"
  12,27,"aur agar is ka kameez peechay se phataa ho to aurat jhooti hai aur yeh sacha """
  12,28,"jab shohar ne dekha ke yousuf ka kameez peechay se phataa hai to is ne kaha"" yeh tum aurton ki chalakiyan hain, waqai barr y ghazab ki hoti hain tumhari chaalein"
  12,29,"yousuf, is muamlay se dar guzar kar aur ae aurat, to apne qasoor ki maffi maang, to hi asal mein khata car thi """
  12,30,"shehar ki aurtain aapas mein charcha karne lagen ke"" Aziz ki biwi apne nojawan ghulam ke peechay pari hui hai, mohabbat ne is ko be qaboo kar rakha hai, hamaray nazdeek to woh Sarih ghalti kar rahi hai """
  12,31,"is ne jo unn ki yeh makkarana baatein sunen to unn ko bulawa bhaij diya aur un ke liye takiya daar majlis aaraasta ki aur ziyafat mein har aik ke agay aik churee rakh di ( phir ain is waqt jabkay woh phal kaat kaat kar kha rahi theen ) is ne yousuf ko ishara kya ke un ke samnay nikal aa jab un aurton ki nigah is par pari to woh dang reh gayeen aur apne haath kaat bathain aur be sakhta pakka ray utheen"" HaaSha-Allahہ, yeh shakhs ensaan nahi hai, yeh to koi buzurag farishta hai """
  12,32,"Aziz ki biwi ne kaha"" dekh liya! yeh hai yeh woh shakhs jis ke maamla mein tum mujh par baatein banati theen be shak mein ne isay rijhaane ki koshish ki thi magar yeh bach nikla agar yeh mera kehna nah manay ga to qaid kya jaye ga aur bohat zaleel o khawar hoga"
  12,33,"yousuf ne kaha"" ae mere rab, qaid mujhe Manzoor hai bah nisbat is ke ke mein woh kaam karoon jo yeh log mujh se chahtay hain aur agar to ne un ki chalon ko mujh se dafaa nah kya to mein un ke daam mein phas jaoon ga aur jahilon mein shaamil ho rahon ga"
  12,34,"is ke rab ne is ki dua qubool ki aur unn aurton ki chaalein is se dafaa kar den, be shak wohi hai jo sab ki santa aur sab kuch jaanta hai"
  12,35,phir un logon ko yeh sojhi ke aik muddat ke liye usay qaid kar den halaank woh ( is ki pakdamni aur khud apni aurton ke buray atwaar ki ) Sarih nishanain dekh chuke thay
  12,36,"qaid khanah mein do ghulam aur bhi is ke sath daakhil hue aik roz unn mein se aik ne uss se kaha"" mein ne khawab mein dekha hai ke mein sharaab kasheed kar raha hon"" dosray ne kaha"" mein ne dekha ke mere sir par rotian rakhi hain aur parinday un ko kha rahay hain"" dono ne kaha"" hamein is ki tabeer bataiye, hum dekhte hain ke aap aik naik aadmi hain """
  12,37,"yousuf ne kaha :"" yahan jo khana tumhe mila karta hai is ke anay se pehlay mein tumhe inn khowaboon ki tabeer bta dun ga yeh ilm unn aloom mein se hai jo mere rab ne mujhe ataa kiye hain waqea yeh hai ke mein ne unn logon ka tareeqa chore kar jo Allah par imaan nahi laatay aur akhirat ka inkaar karte hain"
  12,38,"apne buzurgon, ibrahim, ishaq aur yaqoob ka tareeqa ikhtiyar kya hai hamara yeh kaam nahi hai ke Allah ke sath kisi ko shareektehraئیں Dur haqeeqat yeh Allah ka fazl hai hum par aur tamam insanon par ( ke is ne apne siwa kisi ka bandah hamein nahi banaya ) magar aksar log shukar nahi karte"
  12,39,"ae zandan ke ساتھیو, tum khud hi socho ke bohat se mutafarraq rab behtar hain ya woh aik Allah jo sab ghalib hai ?"
  12,40,"uss ko chore kar tum jin ki bandagi kar rahay ho woh is ke siwa kuch nahi hain ke bas chand naam hain jo tum ne aur tumahray abao ajdaad ne rakh liye hain, Allah ne un ke liye koi sanad nazil nahi ki farmaa rawai ka Iqtidaar Allah ke siwa kisi ke liye nahi hai is ka hukum hai ke khud is ke siwa tum kisi ki bandagi nah karo yahi theth seedha tareeq zindagi hai, magar aksar log jantay nahi hain"
  12,41,"ae zandan ke sathiyo, tumahray khawab ki tabeer yeh hai ke tum mein se aik to apne rab ( Shah misar ) ko sharaab pilaaye ga, raha dosra to usay suli par charhaya jaye ga aur parinday is ka sir noch noch kar khayen ge faisla ho gaya uss baat ka jo tum pooch rahay thay """
  12,42,"phir unn mein se jis ke mutaliq khayaal tha ke woh raha ho jaye ga is se yousuf ne kaha ke"" apne rab ( Shah misar ) se mera zikar karna"" magar shetan ne usay aisa ghaflat mein dala ke woh apne rab ( Shah misar ) se is ka zikar karna bhool gaya aur yousuf kayi saal qaid khanaay mein para raha"
  12,43,"aik roz badshah ne kaha"" mein ne khawab mein dekha hai ke saat mouti ghaein hain jin ko saat dubli ghaein kha rahi hain, aur anaaj ki saat balen hari hain aur doosri saat sookhi ae ahal darbaar, mujhe is khawab ki tabeer batao agar tum khowaboon ka matlab samajte ho """
  12,44,"logon ne kaha"" yeh to pareshan khowaboon ki baatein hain aur hum is terhan ke khowaboon ka matlab nahi jantay """
  12,45,"unn do qaidyoun mein se jo shakhs bach gaya tha aur ussay aik muddat daraaz ke baad ab baat yaad aayi, uss ne kaha"" mein aap hazraat ko is ki taweel batata hon, mujhe zara ( qaid khanaay mein yousuf ke paas ) bhaij degiye """
  12,46,"is ne ja kar kaha"" yousuf, ae saraapaa raasti, mujhe is khawab ka matlab bta ke saat mouti ghaein jin ko saat dubli ghaein kha rahi hain aur saat balen hari hain aur saat sookhi shayad ke mein unn logon ke paas jaoon aur shayad ke woh jaan len """
  12,47,"yousuf ne kaha"" saat Bar seen taq lagataar tum log khaiti baari karte raho ge is douran mein jo faslein tum katu unn mein se bas thora sahissah, jo tumhari khoraak ke kaam aeye, nikalu aur baqi ko is ki balon hi mein rehne do"
  12,48,phir saat baras bohat sakht ayen ge uss zamane mein woh sab ghalla kha liya jaye ga jo tum uss waqt ke liye jama karo ge agar kuch bachay ga to bas wohi jo tum ne mehfooz kar rakha ho
  12,49,"is ke baad phir aik saal aisa aeye ga jis mein baaraan rehmat se logon ki faryaad rassi ki jaye gi aur woh ras nachorain ge """
  12,50,"badshah ne kaha usay mere paas lao magar jab Shahi Farstada yousuf ke paas pouncha to is ne kaha"" apne rab ke paas wapas ja aur is se pooch ke unn aurton ka kya maamla hai jinhon ne apne haath kaat liye thay? mera rab to un ki makkari se waaqif hi hai """
  12,51,"is par badshah ne un aurton se daryaft kya"" tumhara kya tajurbah hai uss waqt ka jab tum ne yousuf ko rijhaane ki koshish ki thi ?"" sab ne yak zabaan ho kar kaha"" Haa- sha- Allah, hum ne to uss mein badi ka shaiyba taq nah paaya"" Aziz ki biwi bol uthi"" ab haq khil chuka hai, woh mein hi thi jis ne uss ko پھسلانے ki koshish ki thi, be shak woh bilkul sacha hai """
  12,52,"( yousuf ne kaha )"" iss se meri gharz yeh thi ke ( Aziz ) yeh jaan le ke mein ne darparda is ki khayanat nahi ki thi, aur yeh ke jo khayanat karte hain un ki chalon ko Allah kamyabi ki raah par nahi lagaata"
  12,53,"mein kuch apne nafs ki براءت nahi kar raha hon, nafs to badi par aksata hi hai ila yeh ke kisi par mere rab ki rehmat ho, be shak mera rab bara ghafoor o Raheem hai """
  12,54,"badshah ne kaha"" unhen mere paas lao taakay mein un ko apne liye makhsoos kar lon"" jab yousuf ne is se guftagu ki to is ne kaha"" ab aap hamaray haan qader o manzilat rakhtay hain aur aap ki amanat par poora bhrosa hai """
  12,55,"yousuf ne kaha,"" malik ke khazanay mere supurd kiijiye, mein hifazat karne wala bhi hon aur ilm bhi rakhta hon """
  12,56,"iss terhan hum ne uss sarzamen mein yousuf ke liye Iqtidaar ki raah hamwar ki woh mukhtaar tha ke is mein jahan chahay apni jagah banaye hum apni rehmat se jis ko chahtay hain nawaazte hain, naik logon ka ajar hamaray haan mara nahi jata"
  12,57,aur akhirat ka ajar unn logo n ke liye ziyada behtar hai jo imaan le aeye aur khuda tarsi ke sath kaam karte rahay
  12,58,yousuf ke bhai misar aeye aur is ke haan haazir hue is ne inhen pehchan liya magar woh is se na aashna thay
  12,59,"phir jab is ne un ka samaan tayyar karwa diya to chaltay waqt un se kaha,"" apne soutelay bhai ko mere paas lana dekhte nahi ho ke mein kis terhan pemana bhar kar deta hon aur kaisa acha mehman Nawaz hon"
  12,60,"agar tum usay nah lao ge to mere paas tumahray liye koi ghalla nahi hai balkay tum mere qareeb bhi nah phatakna """
  12,61,"unhon ne kaha,"" hum koshish karen ge ke waalid sahib usay bhejnay par razi ho jayen, aur hum aisa zaroor karen ge """
  12,62,"yousuf ne apne ghulamoo ko ishara kya ke"" inn logon ne ghallay ke aiwz jo maal diya hai woh chupkay se un ke samaan hi mein rakh do"" yeh yousuf ne iss umeed par kya ke ghar poanch kar woh apna wapas paaya howa maal pehchan jayen ge ( ya iss Fayazi par ahsaan mand hon ge ) aur ajab nahi ke phir pultayn"
  12,63,"jab woh apne baap ke paas gay to kaha"" abba jaan, aindah hum ko ghalla dainay se inkaar kar diya gaya hai, lehaza aap hamaray bhai ko hamaray sath bhaij degiye taakay hum ghalla le kar ayen aur is ki hifazat ke hum zimma daar hain """
  12,64,"baap ne jawab diya"" kya mein uss ke maamla mein tum par waisa hi bharosa karoon jaissa iss se pehlay uss ke bhai ke maamla mein kar chuka hon? Allah hi behtar Muhafiz hai aur woh sab se barh kar reham frmane wala hai """
  12,65,"phir jab unhon ne apna samaan khoola to dekha ke un ka maal bhi inhen wapas kar diya gaya hai yeh dekh kar woh pukaar utthay"" abba jaan, aur hamein kya chahiye, dekhieye yeh hamara maal bhi hamein wapas day diya gaya hai bas ab hum jayen ge aur apne ahal o Ayal ke liye rasad le ayen ge, apne bhai ki hifazat bhi karen ge aur aik bar-e- shutar (ount ka wazan) aur ziyada bhi le ayen ge, itnay ghalla ka izafah aasani ke sath ho jaye ga """
  12,66,"un ke baap ne kaha"" mein is ko hargiz tumahray sath nah beju ga jab taq ke tum Allah ke naam se mujh ko Paiman nah day do ke isay mere pa seen zaroor wapas le kar aao ge ila yeh ke kahin tum ghair hi liye jao"" jab unhon ne is ko apne apne Paiman day diye to is ne kaha"" dekho, hamaray is qoul par Allah nigehbaan hai """
  12,67,"phir is ne kaha"" mere bachcho, misar ke darul-saltanat mein aik darwazay se daakhil nah hona balkay mukhtalif darwazon se jana magar mein Allah ki Mushiyat se tum ko nahi bacha sakta, hukum uss ke siwa kisi ka bhi nahi chalta, isi par mein ne bharosa kya, aur jis ko bhi bharosa karna ho isi par kere """
  12,68,aur waqea bhi yahi howa ke jab woh apne baap ki hadaayat ke mutabiq shehar mein ( mutafarraq darwazon se ) daakhil hue to is ki yeh ahteyati tadbeer Allah ki Mushiyat ke muqablay mein kuch bhi kaam nah aaski haan bas yaqoob ke dil mein jo aik khatak thi usay daur karne ke liye is ne apni si koshish kar li be shak woh hamari di hui taleem se sahib ilm tha magar aksar log maamla ki haqeeqat ko jantay nahi hain
  12,69,"yeh log yousuf ke huzoor puhanche to is ne apne bhai ko apne paas allag bulaa liya aur usay bta diya ke"" mein tera wohi bhai hon ( jo khoya gaya tha ) ab to unn baton ka gham nah kar jo yeh log karte rahay hain """
  12,70,"jab yousuf un bhaiyon ka samaan ladwanaylaga to is ne apne bhai ke samaan mein apna pyalaa rakh diya phir aik pukarnay walay ne pukaar kar kaha"" ae qaafley walo, tum lau g chor ho """
  12,71,"unhon ne palat kar poocha"" tumhari kya cheez khoyi gayi? """
  12,72,"sarkari mulazimo ne kaha"" badshah ka pemana hum ko nahi milta"" ( aur un ke jamadaar ne kaha )"" jo shakhs laa kar day ga uss ke liye aik bar-Shutar (ount ka wazan)inaam hai, is ka mein zimma laita hon """
  12,73,"un bhaiyon ne kaha"" khuda ki qasam, to log khoob jantay ho ke hum is malik mein fasaad karne nahi aeye hain aur hum choryan karne walay log nahi hain """
  12,74,"onhon ne kaha"" acha, agar tumhari baat jhooti niklee to chor ki kya saza hai? """
  12,75,"onhon ne kaha"" uss ki saza? jis ke samaan mein se cheez niklay woh aap hi apni saza mein rakh liya jaye, hamaray haan to aisay zaalmon ko saza dainay ka yahi tareeqa hai """
  12,76,"tab yousuf ne apne bhai se pehlay unn ki kharjion ki talashi leni shuru ki, phir apne bhai ki kharji se gum shuda cheez bar aamad kar li iss terhan hum ne yousuf ki taied apni tadbeer se ki uss ka yeh kaam nah tha ke badshah ke deen ( yani misar ke Shahi qanoon ) mein apne bhai ko pokarta ila yeh ke Allah hi aisa chahay hum jis ke darjay chahtay hain buland kar dete hain, aur aik ilm rakhnay wala aisa hai jo har sahib ilm se baala tar hai"
  12,77,"un bhaiyon ne kaha"" yeh chori kere to kuch taajjub ki baat bhi nahi, is se pehlay is ka bhai ( yousuf ) bhi chori kar chuka hai"" yousuf un ki yeh baat sun kar pi gaya, haqeeqat un par nah kholi bas ( zair lab ) itna keh kar reh gaya ke"" barray hi buray ho tum log, ( mere mun Dur mun mujh par ) jo ilzaam tum laga rahay ho is ki haqeeqat khuda khoob jaanta hai """
  12,78,"unhon ne kaha"" ae sardar Zee Iqtidaar ( Aziz ), is ka baap bohat boorha aadmi hai, is ki jagah aap hum mein se kisi ko rakh lijiye, hum aap ko bara hi naik nafs ensaan paate hain """
  12,79,"yousuf ne kaha"" panah ba khuda, dosray kisi shakhs ko hum kaisay rakh satke hain jis ke paas hum ne apna maal paaya hai is ko chore kar dosray ko rakhen ge to hum zalim hon ge """
  12,80,"jab woh yousuf se mayoos ho gay to aik gooshay mein ja kar aapas mein mahswara karne lagey un mein jo sab se bara tha woh bola"" tum jantay nahi ho ke tumahray waalid tum se khuda ke naam par kya ehad o Paiman le chuke hain aur is se pehlay yousuf ke maamla mein jo zayad-ti tum kar chuke ho woh bhi tum ko maloom hai ab mein to yahan se hargiz nah jaoon ga jab taq ke mere waalid mujhe ijazat nah den, ya phir Allah hi mere haq mein koi faisla farma day ke woh sab se behtar faisla karne wala hai"
  12,81,"tum ja kar apne waalid se kaho ke"" abba jaan, aap ke sahibzaday ne chori ki hai hum ne usay chori karte hue nahi dekha, jo kuch hamein maloom howa hai bas wohi hum bayan kar rahay hain, aur ghaib ki nigehbani to hum nah kar satke thay"
  12,82,"aap uss bastii ke logon se pooch lijiye jahan hum thay uss qaafley se daryaft kar lijiye jis ke sath hum aeye hain hum apne bayan mein bilkul sachey hain """
  12,83,"baap ne yeh daastaa’n sun kar kaha"" darasal tumahray nafs ne tumahray liye aik aur barri baat ko sahal bana diya acha is par bhi sabr karoon ga aur bakhoobi karoon ga kya baeed hai ke Allah un sab ko mujh se laa mila ye, woh sab kuch jaanta hai aur is ke sab kaam hikmat par mabni hain """
  12,84,"phir woh un ki taraf se mun phair kar baith gaya aur kehnay laga ke"" ha ye Yousuf !"" woh dil hi dil mein gham se ghata ja raha tha aur is ki ankhen safaid par gayi theen"
  12,85,"beton ne kaha"" khudaaraa! aap to bas Yousuf hi ko yaad kiye jatay hain nobat yeh aa gayi hai ke is ke gham mein apne aap ko ghulla den ge ya apni jaan halaak kar dalain ge """
  12,86,"uss ne kaha"" mein apni pareshani aur apne gham ki faryaad Allah ke siwa kisi se nahi karta, aur Allah se jaissa mein waaqif hon tum nahi ho"
  12,87,"mere bachcho, ja kar yousuf aur is ke bhai ki kuch tooh lagao, Allah ki rehmat se mayoos nah ho, is ki rehmat se to bas kafir hi mayoos howa karte hain """
  12,88,"jab yeh log misar ja kar yousuf ki paishi mein daakhil hue to unhon ne arz kya ke"" ae sardar ba Iqtidaar , hum aur hamaray ahal o Ayal sakht museebat mein mubtala hain aur hum kuch haqeer si poonji le kar aeye hain, aap hamein bhar poor ghalla inayat farmaen aur hum ko khairaat den, Allah khairaat karne walon ko jaza deta hai """
  12,89,"( yeh sun کریوسف se nah raha gaya ) uss ne kaha"" tumhe kuch yeh bhi maloom hai ke tum ne yousuf aur uss ke bhai ke sath kya kya tha jabkay tum nadaan thay """
  12,90,"woh choank kar bolay"" kya tum yousuf ho ?"" uss ne kaha,"" haan, mein yousuf hon aur yeh mera bhai hai Allah ne hum par ahsaan farmaya haqeeqat yeh hai ke agar koi taqwa aur sabr se kaam le to Allah ke haan aisay naik logon ka ajar mara nahi jata """
  12,91,"unhon ne kaha"" ba khuda ke tum ko Allah ne hum par fazeelat bakhsh aur waqai hum khata car thay """
  12,92,"is ne jawab diya,"" aaj tum par koi girift nahi, Allah tumhe maaf kere, woh sab se barh kar reham frmane wala hai"
  12,93,"jao, mera yeh kameez le jao aur mere waalid ke mun par daal do, unn ki benaye palat aeye gi, aur apne sab ahal o Ayal ko mere paas le aao """
  12,94,"jab yeh qaafla ( misar se ) rawana howa to un ke baap ne ( canaan mein ) kaha"" mein yousuf ki khusbhoo mehsoos kar raha hon, tum log kahin yeh nah kehnay lagu ke mein burhapay mein sathya gaya hon """
  12,95,"ghar ke log bolay"" khuda ki qasam aap abhi taq apne isi puranay khabt mein parre hue hain """
  12,96,"phir jab khoo sh khaberi laane wala aaya to is ne yousuf ka kameez yaqoob ke munh par daal diya aur yaka yak is ki benaye Aud kar aayi tab is ne kaha"" mein tum se kehta nah tha? mein Allah ki taraf se woh kuch jaanta hon jo tum nahi jantay """
  12,97,"sab bol utthay"" abba jaan, aap hamaray gunaaho ki bakhshish ke liye dua karen, waqai hum khata car thay """
  12,98,"uss ne kaha"" mein apne rab se tumahray liye maffi ki darkhwast karoon ga, woh bara maaf karne wala aur Raheem hai """
  12,99,"phir jab yeh log yousuf ke paas puhanche to uss ne apne walidain ko apne sath bitha liya aur ( apne sab knbe walon se ) kaha"" chalo, ab shehar mein chalo, Allah ne chaha to aman chain se raho ge """
  12,100,"( shehar mein daakhil honay ke baad ) is ne apne walidain ko utha kar apne paas takhat par bithaya aur sab is ke agay be ikhtiyar sjday mein jhuk gay yousuf ne kaha"" abba jaan, yeh tabeer hai mere uss khawab ki jo mein ne pehlay dekha tha, mere rab ne usay haqeeqat bana diya is ka ahsaan hai ke uss ne mujhe qaid khanaay se nikala, aur aap logon ko sehraa se laa kar mujh se milaya halaank shetan mere aur mere bhaiyon ke darmain fasaad daal chuka tha waqea yeh hai ke mera rab ghair mehsoos tadbeeron se apni Mushiyat poori karta hai, be shak o hay Aleem aur hakeem hai"
  12,101,"ae mere rab, to ne mujhe hukoomat bakhsh aur mujh ko baton ki teh taq pohanchna sikhaya zameen o aasman ke bananay walay, to hi duniya aur akhirat mein mera sarparast hai, mera khtama islam par kar aur injaam car mujhe salheenke sath mila """
  12,102,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, yeh qissa ghaib ki khabron mein se hai jo hum tum par wahi kar rahay hain warna tum uss waqt mojood nah thay jab yousuf ke bhaiyon ne aapas mein ittafaq kar ke saazish ki thi"
  12,103,magar tum khuwa kitna hi chaho inn mein se aksar log maan kar dainay walay nahi hain
  12,104,halaank tum is khidmat par un se koi ujrat bhi nahi mangte ho yeh to aik nasiyaat hai jo duniya walon ke liye aam hai
  12,105,zameen aur asmano mein kitni hi nishanain hain jin par se yeh log guzarte rehtay hain aur zara tavajja nahi karte
  12,106,un mein se aksar Allah ko mantay hain magar is terhan ke uss ke sath dosaron ko shareektehratay hain
  12,107,kya yeh mutmaen hain ke khuda ke azaab ki koi bulaa inhen daboch nah le gi ya be khaberi mein qayamat ki gharri achanak un par nah aa jaye gi ?
  12,108,"tum un se saaf keh do ke"" mera rasta to yeh hai, mein Allah ki taraf bulaataa hon, mein khud bhi poori roshni mein apna rasta dekh raha hon aur mere saathi bhi, aur Allah pak hai aur shirk karne walon se mera koi vaastaa nahi """
  12,109,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum se pehlay hum ne jo paighambar beje thay woh sab bhi ensaan hi thay, aur unhi bustiyon ke rehne walon mein se thay, aur aُnhi ki taraf hum wahi bhaijtay rahay hain phir kya yeh log zameen mein chalay phiray nahi hain ke unn qomon ka injaam inhen nazar nah aaya jo un se pehlay guzar chuki hain? yaqeenan akhirat ka ghar unn logon ke liye aur ziyada behtar hai jinhon ne ( payghambaroon ki baat maan kar ) taqwa ki rawish ikhtiyar ki kya ab bhi tum log nah samjhoo ge ?"
  12,110,"( pehlay payghambaroon ke sath bhi yahi hota raha hai ke woh muddaton nasiyaat karte rahay aur logon ne sun kar nah diya ) yahan taq ke jab paighambar logon se mayoos ho gay aur logon ne bhi samajh liya ke unn se jhoot bola gaya tha, to yaka yak hamari madad payghambaroon ko poanch gayi phir jab aisa mauqa aa jata hai to hamara qaida yeh hai ke jisay hum chahtay hain bacha letay hain aur mujrimon par se to hamara azaab taalla hi nahi ja sakta"
  12,111,aglay logon ke un qisson mein aqal o hosh rakhnay walon ke liye Ibrat hai yeh jo kuch quran mein bayan kya ja raha hai yeh banawati baatein nahi hain balkay jo kitaaben is se pehlay aayi hui hain unhi ki tasdeeq hai aur har cheez ki tafseel aur imaan laane walon ke liye hadaayat aur rehmat
